Vorbis is a public-domain, patent-free, lossy audio compression format usually
paired with the Ogg file format. libvorbis is the official encoder/decoder
library for the Vorbis audio format.

libvorbis is the full floating-point codec library for Vorbis and must be used
with libogg. For KOS-specific support, please use these two libraries along with
the liboggvorbisplay library.

URL: http://www.vorbis.com/
